# R serialization fixtures must never go through line-ending conversion:
# an ASCII-mode RData (save(ascii = TRUE) implies compress = FALSE) contains
# no NUL bytes, so git's heuristic classifies it as text and a Windows
# checkout with core.autocrlf=true corrupts it by rewriting LF to CRLF.
*.rds binary
*.RData binary
*.rdata binary
*.rda binary
*.RDA binary
*.pyd binary
